This is in accordance with Technical Guidance  for Certifications & Audit under real Estate (Regulation & Development)Act, 2016 issued by ICAI we have reduced the interest cost on partners capital from the cost incurred and paid.
3.	We are unable to certify the detail of PAN no and Mobile number of the customer, since the necessary evidence is not in the possession of the firm.
4. Further, I am unable to certify as to whether the firm had entered registered agreement for sale with buyers on receipt of consideration In excess of 10% of the apartment value.
